&lt;p&gt;One of our teams is looking for a new teammate. They are focusing on bringing AI into real products - not as a toy, but as something that actually solves problems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll be working on practical use of LLMs and AI approaches in a product environment. That means experimenting, validating ideas, and helping teams understand what works and what doesn’t. You won’t be sitting in a research silo - you’ll be working directly with teams and helping turn ideas into something usable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’d like to work remotely, no problem. We’re used to hybrid collaboration based on team agreement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE OFFER:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Things to be fresh. We’re building new AI products just now - and you can be part of the journey from start to finish. You’ll work across a wide range of AI disciplines, from text processing through image analysis to process automation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No coding monkeys. We experiment, question, and figure things out.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work that starts with an idea and ends in a real product.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A manager-less structure. No hierarchy, everyone has a say.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A team that decides. Hiring, promotions, direction - all in the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No bulls**t KPIs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learning and knowledge sharing is part of the job, not a side activity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE EXPECT FROM YOU:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Python&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with at least one &lt;strong&gt;AI / ML-related project&lt;/strong&gt; (school, personal, or work)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic understanding of:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;datasets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;statistics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;good practices in data/ML work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interest in AI beyond just LLMs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to explain things and share knowledge with others&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be open-minded&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Come up with improvements and realize them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Share your knowledge with others&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Readiness to learn new things&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NICE TO HAVE:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with LLMs (RAG, agents, fine-tuning…)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with AI frameworks or tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Any exposure to production systems or cloud&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;form-text-top&quot;&gt;Haven´t found what you´re looking for among our open positions?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;form-text-top&quot;&gt;Don´t worry. Fill in this form and keep in touch.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;form-text-top&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;form-text-bottom&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We&#39;re&amp;nbsp;expanding our R&amp;amp;D division, opening 30 positions for programmers looking to work with Cloud and AI. Join our existing 130 developers, spread across 18 teams, in a unique managerless organization&amp;nbsp;that&#39;s&amp;nbsp;all about individual responsibility, trust, and solving real problems (not just&amp;nbsp;cranking out&amp;nbsp;code).&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Whether you’re a seasoned junior or a senior-level dev, what matters the most is your technical curiosity, eagerness to learn across domains, and motivation to keep pushing the team and yourself forward.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE OFFER:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A manager-less structure.&lt;/strong&gt; No micromanagement. No status pyramids. Everyone has a say, and it counts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Full-stack experience.&lt;/strong&gt; You can shape the product from UI to backend and cloud orchestration. We’re not boxed into roles.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A “stuff diving” &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;mindset.&lt;/strong&gt; We work with what’s needed, apply the right principles, and carry lessons across technologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Freedom to grow.&lt;/strong&gt; If you like exploring new things like DevOps, functional programming, frontends, whatever we’ve got space for it.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Peer-driven culture.&lt;/strong&gt; We build things together, review each other’s code, and hold regular knowledge-sharing sessions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Home office is not a benefit; it is a standard&lt;/strong&gt; – we are used to working in a hybrid model, based on team agreement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE EXPECT FROM YOU:&lt;br&gt;Must have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Java proficiency&lt;/strong&gt;, or solid experience with another &lt;strong&gt;OOP language&lt;/strong&gt; and a willingness to switch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Genuine interest in functional programming. &lt;/strong&gt;Scala is our backend language of choice, and we’ll help you get there&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience and interest in AI -&lt;/strong&gt; Our strategy focuses on robust automation that blends innovative research with real-world enterprise needs, moving beyond basic chatbot integration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Readiness to &lt;strong&gt;drive things forward&lt;/strong&gt;, whether it be through tech exploration, pair programming, or sharing your insights&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to switch context and stay comfortable outside a single tech stack&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curiosity, responsibility, and a desire to &lt;strong&gt;get things done&lt;/strong&gt;, not because you’re told, but because it excites joy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluent in Czech/Slovak + English at least B2&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with any &lt;strong&gt;functional or multi-paradigm language&lt;/strong&gt;: Scala, JavaScript, Python, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;DevOps awareness: Kubernetes, ArgoCD, Bamboo, shell scripting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Do you crave more information and technologies we work with? ® &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.ysoft.com/careers/develop-with-us&quot;&gt;Develop with us&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

